    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing... it doesn't feel like an illness. it feels more like a truth. if the music and the color are gone, then there isn't actually a person here anymore. just this heavy, breathing thing that takes up space and consumes resources. it feels so pointless to keep maintaining a vessel that has nothing left to hold.",
